The evidence with the title 'PolitiFact's lie of the year: 'a government takeover of health care ... ' says Dec 16, 2010  ... The claim that the Democratic health care law is a " government takeover of health care " is our 2010 Lie Of The Year. In the spring of 2009, a Republican strategist settled on a brilliant and powerful attack line for president Barack Obama 's ambitious plan to overhaul America 's health insurance system. 
